  <p>
    If we extrapolate this to the 145 courses listed above, we find there is a need for 48 FTE of
    OER revision labor every 4 years. Or 12 FTE each year. If we assume that some of this labor is
    covered by FT faculty <q>service to the college</q>, it is reasonable to round down to 10 FTE.
  </p>
  <p>
    Of course, this is a rough extrapolation, and OERs from the 145 courses mentioned above might
    need more or less than the extrapolation assumes.
  </p>
